# Left hand (movement + dodge):

# A / D → Move left/right
# W / S → Up (ladders/look) / Down (crouch/fast fall)
# Space → Jump
# Left Shift → Roll/Dodge (the most important Souls mechanic – easy pinky spam)

# Right hand (combat – super quick access):

# J → Light/Primary Attack
# K → Heavy Attack or Skill
# L → Block/Parry (hold or tap)

# Utility keys (thumb/index easy):

# F or E → Heal / Flask / Use item
# E or Q → Interact / Talk / Pick up
